<div class="calendaria chat-release">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="https://www.patreon.com/3deathsaves" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on Patreon!</a></strong>
    </p>

    <h4>Bug Fixes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Cinematic not playing on long rest</li>
      <li>Cycle stages advancing every unit instead of respecting length</li>
      <li>Darkness flickering on sub-hour time advances</li>
      <li>Equinox/solstice festival notes on wrong dates</li>
      <li>Moon phases wrong when yearZero is non-zero</li>
      <li>Preset manager labels shifting on select/reset/restore</li>
      <li>Reminders with "Notify Before" of 0 not firing</li>
      <li>Settings import failing between worlds</li>
      <li>Weather breaking at extreme temperatures</li>
      <li>Weather sounds persisting when scene FX disabled</li>
      <li>Weekday reorder not persisting after save</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Improvements</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Season temp range is now the authority for weather generation</li>
      <li>Default preset can sync to imported/uncategorized notes</li>
      <li>New <code>calendaria.rendered</code> hook fires after all apps are visible</li>
      <li>Widgets registered during <code>calendaria.ready</code> appear on first render</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <a class="open-note" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
